Why would a country adopt Apollo?

- To empower citizens to take better care of themselves
- To reduce the socioeconomic burden of lower extremity dysfunction


How would a country adopt Apollo?

- Public health education campaigns
- Free online education resources for citizens
- Teach principles within national physical education curriculum 
- Chair free classrooms
- Educate about unnatural inputs and natural inputs
- Teach first principles of biology
- Create a national health professional academy
- Mandatory curriculum within post graduate health professional programs
